{"text_id":170458,"tokens":["A"," team"," of"," engineers"," in"," Korea"," has"," designed"," a"," new"," Virtual"," Reality"," glove"," that"," can"," create"," the"," sensation"," of"," touch"," when"," manipulating"," digital"," objects","."," VR"," gloves"," are"," not"," new",","," but"," this"," one"," adds"," a"," significant"," level"," of"," dexterity"," to"," the"," mix","."," The"," glove"," consists"," of"," two"," main"," parts",":"," the"," glove"," itself"," and"," a"," separate"," controller","."," The"," controller"," is"," a"," PS","VR"," controller"," that"," is"," attached"," to"," the"," glove"," by"," a"," rigid"," tube","."," It"," also"," has"," several"," sensors"," that"," are"," used"," to"," sense"," the"," hand","'","s"," position",","," and"," determines"," which"," finger"," has"," touched"," the"," surface","."," The"," sensor"," is"," used"," to"," calculate"," how"," far"," the"," user","'","s"," finger"," has"," moved"," from"," its"," starting"," position",","," and"," the"," amount"," of"," force"," that"," was"," applied","."," The"," sensors"," are"," also"," used"," to"," detect"," the"," type"," of"," force"," applied",","," which"," allows"," the"," user"," to"," feel"," which"," finger"," has"," been"," used"," to"," tap"," the"," virtual"," object","."," The"," glove"," itself"," is"," ","3","D"," printed",","," and"," it"," is"," removable","."," It"," has"," a"," silicone"," inner"," lining"," that"," is"," designed"," to"," feel"," comfortable",","," and"," the"," fingertips"," have"," a"," metallic"," coating"," that"," is"," used"," to"," detect"," touches","."," The"," team"," is"," looking"," at"," ways"," to"," integrate"," the"," glove"," with"," the"," Oculus"," Rift",","," which"," is"," a"," motion","-","tracking"," headset","."," Using"," this"," combination"," would"," allow"," users"," to"," manipulate"," objects"," in"," virtual"," environments"," in"," a"," completely"," immersive"," way","."," This"," is"," a"," great"," example"," of"," how"," researchers"," are"," using"," new"," technologies"," to"," enhance"," the"," virtual"," reality"," experience","."," We"," have"," seen"," a"," lot"," of"," improvements"," in"," the"," past"," few"," years",","," but"," this"," one"," stands"," out"," to"," us"," because"," it"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," make"," us"," feel"," even"," more"," immersed","."," We"," are"," in"," the"," early"," stages"," of"," VR"," technology",","," and"," it"," is"," important"," to"," keep"," experimenting"," with"," new"," ideas","."," We"," are"," sure"," that"," there"," are"," more"," innovations"," to"," come","."],"sub_source":"tldr","model":"7B","label":1}